Welcome to this residence nestled in the Vineyards. This home boasts 5 bedrooms, one that you can transform to meet your unique needs, and 3 bathrooms. As you step inside, you'll notice the expansive living area, plenty of countertop space in the kitchen as well as ample garage space for all your storage needs, you'll have plenty of room for your vehicles and more. 
Schedule a showing today!
